message: Focus on 'soft' ingredients. Always use 'scissors' on soft ingredients first (e.g., flower, ribbon, yarn, sponge, leaf, sunflower, newspaper) to create 'cut' versions; this usually yields 25 points. The most valuable combinations are made by blending a 'cut' natural, soft item with a 'cut' artificial, soft item. For example, combine 'cut flower' (natural, soft, cut) with 'cut ribbon' (artificial, soft, cut) to get 80 points.
